    "body": "Ha, I just a friend say the same exact thing. Behind the scenes, the objects are called \"Shell::PowerShell\" so I'll switch the new one to be `Shell::Pwsh`.\r\n\r\nFor a user who has configured `powershell_indicator` this is probably fine if both look the same, and for folks who want to distinguish they can add something to their config.\r\n\r\nSorry this probably me overthinking (again). ",
